input_str: "Homer the Whopper" is the season premiere of The Simpsons' twenty-first season. It originally aired on the Fox network in the United States on September 27, 2009.[1] In the episode, Comic Book Guy creates a new superhero called Everyman who takes powers from other superheroes.
